    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-08-07T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-08-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="765"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d765">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-08-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 7, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 313.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to state that last week the
                    insurgent faction in the State of Los Andes under Gen. Cipriano Castro was
                    completely defeated by the Government troops in a bloody battle which lasted
                    eighteen hours. The loss of the insurgents is placed at 800 killed and wounded
                    and the Government lost 300.</p>
                <p>This is the end of the disturbances in that section, which was the only part
                    where there was trouble.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William W. Russell.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
